Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
ϕ: Pattern
i: ProofInfo
H: Γ ⊢i ϕ using BasicReasoning
_H: ML_proof_system Γ ϕ
Heq_H: _H = `H
Hpf: ((ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ)^~ BasicReasoning) _H
ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ _H i

  
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
ϕ: Pattern
i: ProofInfo
H: Γ ⊢i ϕ using BasicReasoning
_H: ML_proof_system Γ ϕ
Hpf: ((ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ)^~ BasicReasoning) _H
ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ _H i

  abstract (
    destruct Hpf as [Hpf1 Hpf2 Hpf3 Hpf4];
  destruct i; constructor; simpl in *;
  [set_solver|set_solver|idtac|set_solver];
  (destruct (uses_kt _H); simpl in *; try congruence)).
Defined.

Ltac useBasicReasoning :=
  unfold ProofSystem.derives;
  lazymatch goal with
  | [ |- of_MLGoal (mkMLGoal _ _ _ _ _) ] => apply mlUseBasicReasoning
  | [ |- _ ⊢i _ using _ ] => apply useBasicReasoning
  end.


Tactic Notation "remember_constraint" "as" ident(i') :=
    match goal with
    | [|- (_ ⊢i _ using ?constraint)] => remember constraint as i'
    end.

Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
ϕ₁, ϕ₂: Pattern
i: ProofInfo
H1: Γ ⊢i ϕ₁ using i
H2: Γ ⊢i ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂ using i
ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ₂
  (Modus_ponens Γ ϕ₁ ϕ₂
     (unkeyed
        (let (x, H) := H1 in
         (λ (x0 : ML_proof_system Γ ϕ₁) (_ : ((ProofInfoMeaning
                                                 Γ ϕ₁)^~ i)
                                               x0), x0)
           x H))
     (unkeyed
        (let (x, H) := H2 in
         (λ (x0 : ML_proof_system Γ (ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂)) 
            (_ : ((ProofInfoMeaning Γ (ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂))^~ i)
                   x0), x0) x H))) i

  
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
ϕ₁, ϕ₂: Pattern
i: ProofInfo
H1: Γ ⊢i ϕ₁ using i
H2: Γ ⊢i ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂ using i
ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ₂
  (Modus_ponens Γ ϕ₁ ϕ₂
     (unkeyed
        (let (x, H) := H1 in
         (λ (x0 : ML_proof_system Γ ϕ₁) (_ : ((ProofInfoMeaning
                                                 Γ ϕ₁)^~ i)
                                               x0), x0)
           x H))
     (unkeyed
        (let (x, H) := H2 in
         (λ (x0 : ML_proof_system Γ (ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂)) 
            (_ : ((ProofInfoMeaning Γ (ϕ₁ ---> ϕ₂))^~ i)
                   x0), x0) x H))) i

    abstract(
      simpl;
      destruct H1 as [pf1 Hpf1];
      destruct H2 as [pf2 Hpf2];
      destruct Hpf1,Hpf2;
      constructor; simpl;
      [set_solver|set_solver|(destruct (uses_kt pf1),(uses_kt pf2); simpl in *; congruence)|set_solver]
    ).
  }
Defined.

Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
well_formed A → Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
well_formed A → Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning
 
    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
_1: Γ
⊢i (A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A) --->
   (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
_1: Γ
⊢i (A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A) --->
   (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_2: Γ ⊢i A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A
using BasicReasoning
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
_1: Γ
⊢i (A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A) --->
   (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_2: Γ ⊢i A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_3: Γ ⊢i (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
_1: Γ
⊢i (A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A) --->
   (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_2: Γ ⊢i A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_3: Γ ⊢i (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_4: Γ ⊢i A ---> A ---> A using BasicReasoning
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    
Σ: Signature
Γ: Theory
A: Pattern
WFA: well_formed A
_1: Γ
⊢i (A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A) --->
   (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_2: Γ ⊢i A ---> (A ---> A) ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_3: Γ ⊢i (A ---> A ---> A) ---> A ---> A
using BasicReasoning
_4: Γ ⊢i A ---> A ---> A using BasicReasoning
_5: Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning
Γ ⊢i A ---> A using BasicReasoning

    exact _5.
  Defined.

  
Σ: Signature
evs1, evs2: coEVarSet
svs1, svs2: coSVarSet
kt1, kt2: bool
fp1, fp2: coWfpSet
ProofInfoLe
  (ExGen := evs1, SVSubst := svs1, KT := kt1,
   FP := fp1)
  (ExGen := evs2, SVSubst := svs2, KT := kt2,
   FP := fp2)
→ evs1 ⊆ evs2 ∧ svs1 ⊆ svs2 ∧ kt1 ==> kt2 ∧ fp1 ⊆ fp2

  
Σ: Signature
evs1, evs2: coEVarSet
svs1, svs2: coSVarSet
kt1, kt2: bool
fp1, fp2: coWfpSet
ProofInfoLe
  (ExGen := evs1, SVSubst := svs1, KT := kt1,
   FP := fp1)
  (ExGen := evs2, SVSubst := svs2, KT := kt2,
   FP := fp2)
→ evs1 ⊆ evs2 ∧ svs1 ⊆ svs2 ∧ kt1 ==> kt2 ∧ fp1 ⊆ fp2

    
Σ: Signature
evs1, evs2: coEVarSet
svs1, svs2: coSVarSet
kt1, kt2: bool
fp1, fp2: coWfpSet
pile: ProofInfoLe
  (ExGen := evs1, SVSubst := svs1, KT := kt1,
   FP := fp1)
  (ExGen := evs2, SVSubst := svs2, KT := kt2,
   FP := fp2)
evs1 ⊆ evs2 ∧ svs1 ⊆ svs2 ∧ kt1 ==> kt2 ∧ fp1 ⊆ fp2

    
Σ: Signature
evs1, evs2: coEVarSet
svs1, svs2: coSVarSet
kt1, kt2: bool
fp1, fp2: coWfpSet

  (ExGen := evs1, SVSubst := svs1, KT := kt1,
   FP := fp1)
  (ExGen := evs2, SVSubst := svs2, KT := kt2,
   FP := fp2)
evs1 ⊆ evs2

  ((λ (_pattern_value_ : Prop) 
      (_rewrite_rule_ : _pattern_value_ ↔ x = y),
      [eta subrelation_proper
             Morphisms_Prop.not_iff_morphism ()
             (subrelation_respectful
                (subrelation_refl iff)
                (flip2 iff_flip_impl_subrelation))
             _pattern_value_ 
             (x = y)] _rewrite_rule_

           (λ y : evar,

                A_impl_A ∅ 
                  (patt_free_evar y) erefl in

               evar_fresh

                    (free_evars
                       (patt_free_evar x))) in

               e =
               evar_fresh
                 (elements
                    (free_evars
                       (patt_free_evar x))) :=
               erefl in
             let H :
               e ∉ free_evars (patt_free_evar x) :=

                 (free_evars (patt_free_evar x))
                 Heqe in
             nesym
               (let _the_hidden_goal_ := e ≠ x in
                (λ H0 : e ∉ {[x]},
                   unkeyed
                     (not_elem_of_singleton_1 e x
                        H0)) H))
              : x ≠ fresh_evar (patt_free_evar x))
           Heqy)) (x ∈ {[y]})

    (ExGen := evs2, SVSubst := svs2,

Σ: Signature
evs1, evs2: coEVarSet
svs1, svs2: coSVarSet
kt1, kt2: bool
fp1, fp2: coWfpSet
p: Pattern
wfp: well_formed p = true
Hp: p ↾ wfp ∈ fp1
pf1:= A_impl_A ∅ ⊥ erefl: ∅ ⊢i ⊥ ---> ⊥ using BasicReasoning
pf2:= Framing_left ∅ ⊥ ⊥ p wfp
  (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) 
     (⊥ ---> ⊥)
     (ProofSystem.P1 ∅ ⊥ ⊥ erefl erefl)
     (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥)
        ((⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
        (ProofSystem.P1 ∅ ⊥ 
           (⊥ ---> ⊥) erefl
           match
             binary_wfxy_decompose patt_imp 0 0
               (⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥)
               ((⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
               (wf_wfxy00_decompose
                  ((⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥) --->
                   (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) --->
                   ⊥ ---> ⊥)
                  (proved_impl_wf ∅
                     ((⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥) --->
                      (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) --->
                      ⊥ ---> ⊥)
                     (ProofSystem.P2 ∅ ⊥
                        (⊥ ---> ⊥) ⊥ erefl
                        (wf_wfxy00_compose
                        (⊥ ---> ⊥)
                        (binary_wfxy_compose
                        patt_imp 0 0 ⊥ ⊥
                        (conj
                        (wf_wfxy00_decompose ⊥
                        erefl)
                        (wf_wfxy00_decompose ⊥
                        erefl)))) erefl)))
           with
           | conj x x0 =>
               match
                 binary_wfxy_decompose patt_imp 0
                   0 ⊥ ((⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥) x
               with
               | conj _ x2 =>
                   match
                     binary_wfxy_decompose
                       patt_imp 0 0 
                       (⊥ ---> ⊥) ⊥ x2
                   with
                   | conj x3 _ =>
                       match
                        binary_wfxy_decompose
                        patt_imp 0 0 ⊥ ⊥ x3
                       with
                       | conj _ _ =>
                        match
                        binary_wfxy_decompose
                        patt_imp 0 0
                        (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
                        (⊥ ---> ⊥) x0
                        with
                        | conj x7 x8 =>
                        match
                        binary_wfxy_decompose
                        patt_imp 0 0 ⊥ 
                        (⊥ ---> ⊥) x7
                        with

Tactic Notation "gapply" uconstr(pf) := eapply useGenericReasoning;[|eapply pf].

Tactic Notation "gapply" uconstr(pf) "in" ident(H) :=
  eapply useGenericReasoning in H;[|apply pf].


(* Extracts well-formedness assumptions about (local) goal and (local) hypotheses. *)
Tactic Notation "mlExtractWF" ident(wfl) ident(wfg) :=
match goal with
| [ |- ?g ] =>
  let wfl' := fresh "wfl'" in
  let wfg' := fresh "wfg'" in
  intros wfg' wfl';
  pose proof (wfl := wfl');
  pose proof (wfg := wfg');
  revert wfg' wfl';
  fold g;
  rewrite /mlConclusion in wfg;
  rewrite /mlHypotheses in wfl
end.

Γ: Theory
ϕ: Pattern
pf: ML_proof_system Γ ϕ
Hpf2: gset_to_coGset (uses_of_ex_gen Γ ϕ pf) ⊆ ∅
Hpf3: gset_to_coGset (uses_of_svar_subst Γ ϕ pf) ⊆ ∅
Hpf4: uses_kt pf ==> false
pwi_pf_fp: gset_to_coGset (framing_patterns Γ ϕ pf)
⊆ ∅
gset_to_coGset (uses_of_svar_subst Γ ϕ pf) ⊆ svs
 set_solver.

Tactic Notation "_mlReshapeHypsByIdx" constr(n) :=
  unshelve (eapply (@cast_proof_ml_hyps _ _ _ _ _ _ _));
  [shelve|(apply f_equal; rewrite <- (firstn_skipn n); rewrite /firstn; rewrite /skipn; reflexivity)|idtac]
.

Tactic Notation "_mlReshapeHypsByName" constr(n) :=
  unshelve (eapply (@cast_proof_ml_hyps _ _ _ _ _ _ _));
  [shelve|(
    apply f_equal;
    lazymatch goal with
    | [|- _ = ?l] =>
      lazymatch (eval cbv in (find_hyp n l)) with
      | Some (?n, _) =>
        rewrite <- (firstn_skipn n);
        rewrite /firstn;
        rewrite /skipn;
        reflexivity
      end
    end
    )
  |idtac]
.

Ltac2 _mlReshapeHypsByName (name' : constr) :=
  ltac1:(name'' |- _mlReshapeHypsByName name'') (Ltac1.of_constr name')
.

Tactic Notation "_mlReshapeHypsBack" :=
  let hyps := fresh "hyps" in rewrite [hyps in mkMLGoal _ _ hyps _]/app
.

Ltac2 _mlReshapeHypsBack () :=
  ltac1:(_mlReshapeHypsBack)
.

        ∀ x0 : Theory,

             ∀ x2 : Pattern,

Σ: Signature
x: evar
gpi: ProofInfo
svs: coSVarSet
kt: bool
fp: coWfpSet
H: ∀ (Γ : Theory) (ϕ : Pattern) (pf : ML_proof_system
                                     Γ ϕ),
  ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ pf
    (ExGen := {[x]}, SVSubst := svs, KT := kt,
     FP := fp) → ProofInfoMeaning Γ ϕ pf gpi
H1:= A_impl_A ∅ ⊥ erefl: ∅ ⊢i ⊥ ---> ⊥ using BasicReasoning
H2:= prf_add_assumption ∅ (patt_free_evar x) (⊥ ---> ⊥)
  BasicReasoning erefl erefl H1: ∅ ⊢i patt_free_evar x ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥
using BasicReasoning
H3:= Ex_gen ∅ (patt_free_evar x) (⊥ ---> ⊥) x erefl
  erefl
  (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> ⊥)
     (patt_free_evar x ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
     (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) (⊥ ---> ⊥)
        (ProofSystem.P1 ∅ ⊥ ⊥ erefl erefl)
        (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥)
           ((⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
           (ProofSystem.P1 ∅ ⊥ (⊥ ---> ⊥) erefl
              match
                binary_wfxy_decompose patt_imp 0 0
                  (⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥)
                  ((⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)
                  (wf_wfxy00_decompose
                     ((⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥) --->
                      (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥) --->
                      ⊥ ---> ⊥)
                     (proved_impl_wf ∅
                        ((⊥ ---> (⊥ ---> ⊥) ---> ⊥) --->

     (ProofSystem.P1 ∅ (⊥ ---> ⊥)
        (patt_free_evar x)

           (Modus_ponens ∅ (⊥ ---> ⊥ ---> ⊥)

Σ: Signature
gpi: ProofInfo
evs: coEVarSet
svs: coSVarSet
fp: coWfpSet
pf1:= A_impl_A ∅ ⊥ erefl: ∅ ⊢i ⊥ ---> ⊥ using BasicReasoning
pf2:= Knaster_tarski ∅ BoundVarSugar.B0 ⊥ erefl (`pf1): ML_proof_system ∅ ((mu , BoundVarSugar.B0) ---> ⊥)
H1: gset_to_coGset
  (uses_of_ex_gen ∅
     ((mu , BoundVarSugar.B0) ---> ⊥) pf2)
⊆ pi_generalized_evars gpi
H2: gset_to_coGset
  (uses_of_svar_subst ∅
     ((mu , BoundVarSugar.B0) ---> ⊥) pf2)
⊆ pi_substituted_svars gpi
H3: pi_uses_kt gpi
H4: gset_to_coGset
  (framing_patterns ∅
     ((mu , BoundVarSugar.B0) ---> ⊥) pf2)
⊆ pi_framing_patterns gpi
pi_uses_kt gpi
 exact H3.
Qed.
